<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...'cause I was so excited!</b></font>

153
00:13:11,404 --> 00:13:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that feeling.</b></font>

154
00:13:13,904 --> 00:13:17,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't sleep the night before I got my S13.</b></font>

155
00:13:17,844 --> 00:13:23,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't help it, 'cause it's my own car.</b></font>

156
00:13:23,174 --> 00:13:26,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My car... I feel like I'm dreaming...</b></font>

157
00:13:26,944 --> 00:13:29,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'70s tires with original hubcaps...</b></font>

158
00:13:29,284 --> 00:13:31,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So cool!</b></font>

159
00:13:31,354 --> 00:13:33,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you start it up, Itsuki?</b></font>

160
00:13:33,954 --> 00:13:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure thing!</b></font>

161
00:13:47,204 --> 00:13:49,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't sound too sharp...</b></font>

162
00:13:49,474 --> 00:13:52,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It must be because of the original muffler.</b></font>

163
00:13:52,944 --> 00:13:56,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry, I'll get a new muffler.</b></font>

164
00:13:56,144 --> 00:14:00,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want it to sound as cool as Takumi's Trueno.</b></font>

165
00:14:03,254 --> 00:14:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a bad feeling about this.</b></font>

166
00:14:05,024 --> 00:14:07,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pop the hood, Itsuki.</b></font>

167
00:14:23,674 --> 00:14:27,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I knew it...
--Boss?</b></font>

168
00:14:27,504 --> 00:14:29,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You got it all wrong, Itsuki.</b></font>

169
00:14:29,844 --> 00:14:31,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

170
00:14:31,844 --> 00:14:34,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--This isn't an Eight-Six.
--What?</b></font>

171
00:14:34,614 --> 00:14:36,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's an Eight-Five.</b></font>

172
00:14:36,354 --> 00:14:41,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Five... as in AE-85?</b></font>

173
00:14:49,434 --> 00:14:52,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six and an Eight-Five
have the same body,</b></font>

174
00:14:52,234 --> 00:14:56,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but their abilities are as far
apart as chalk is from cheese!</b></font>

175
00:14:56,974 --> 00:14:59,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six has a DOHC engine,</b></font>

176
00:14:59,074 --> 00:15:02,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>while an Eight-Five has an SOHC.</b></font>

177
00:15:02,314 --> 00:15:06,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>DOHC and SOHC are
completely different, you know?</b></font>

178
00:15:06,514 --> 00:15:08,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Didn't you check the engine
before you bought it?</b></font>

179
00:15:08,854 --> 00:15:10,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stupid!</b></font>

180
00:15:15,424 --> 00:15:18,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, Itsuki, but it's funny...</b></font>

181
00:15:18,994 --> 00:15:21,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My stomach hurts!</b></font>

182
00:15:26,404 --> 00:15:28,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, wait!</b></font>

183
00:15:34,514 --> 00:15:36,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You went too far.</b></font>

184
00:15:36,514 --> 00:15:38,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Put yourselves in his position.</b></font>

185
00:15:38,384 --> 00:15:40,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're sorry.</b></font>

186
00:15:43,214 --> 00:15:45,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki!</b></font>

187
00:15:48,054 --> 00:15:50,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just leave me alone, okay?</b></font>

188
00:15:50,754 --> 00:15:53,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't.</b></font>

189
00:15:59,964 --> 00:16:01,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanted to surprise you guys...</b></font>

190
00:16:01,874 --> 00:16:05,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but I was an idiot for buying a car by myself.</b></font>

191
00:16:05,644 --> 00:16:09,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I knew it was too cheap for an Eight-Six.</b></font>

192
00:16:09,144 --> 00:16:14,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm so embarrassed for acting
like an idiot in front of you guys.</b></font>

193
00:16:14,984 --> 00:16:18,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know you're laughing at me inside, too.</b></font>

194
00:16:18,584 --> 00:16:20,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're wrong.</b></font>

195
00:16:20,554 --> 00:16:24,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The fact of the matter is, I envy you.</b></font>

196
00:16:24,664 --> 00:16:26,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You envy me?</b></font>

197
00:16:26,664 --> 00:16:28,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't lie!</b></font>

198
00:16:28,394 --> 00:16:30,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a lie.</b></font>

199
00:16:30,394 --> 00:16:33,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're still in high school,</b></font>

200
00:16:33,234 --> 00:16:36,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and already have your own car.</b></font>

201
00:16:36,034 --> 00:16:38,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--My own car...
--Yeah.</b></font>

202
00:16:38,844 --> 00:16:40,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what if it's an Eight-Five?</b></font>

203
00:16:40,874 --> 00:16:44,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It has an engine and four tires.</b></font>

204
00:16:44,274 --> 00:16:47,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may not have power,
but it'll go fast downhill.</b></font>

205
00:16:47,384 --> 00:16:50,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can still practice your skills.</b></font>

206
00:16:57,724 --> 00:17:00,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Cars are fun...</b></font>

207
00:17:00,464 --> 00:17:04,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You've changed...
--Have I?</b></font>

208
00:17:04,194 --> 00:17:08,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You weren't into cars as much before.</b></font>

209
00:17:08,174 --> 00:17:13,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, I feel like I can
be proud of my Eight-Five.</b></font>

210
00:17:13,904 --> 00:17:18,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I don't deserve an Eight-Six yet.
--You're right.</b></font>

211
00:17:18,744 --> 00:17:22,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't have to agree!</b></font>

212
00:17:22,584 --> 00:17:26,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may go for a spin at Mount Akina tonight.</b></font>

213
00:17:26,484 --> 00:17:28,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wanna come, Takumi?</b></font>

214
00:17:28,054 --> 00:17:31,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure... in your Eight-Five.</b></font>

215
00:17:31,064 --> 00:17:32,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...</b></font>

216
00:17:32,864 --> 00:17:35,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yippee!</b></font>

217
00:17:35,534 --> 00:17:38,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll come get you around 10:00 tonight.</b></font>

218
00:17:38,664 --> 00:17:41,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--Don't fall asleep!</b></font>

219
00:17:48,174 --> 00:17:50,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't see the famous Eight-Six.</b></font>

220
00:17:50,874 --> 00:17:53,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna take a look at it.</b></font>

221
00:17:53,184 --> 00:17:57,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't imagine an R32 losing to an Eight-Six.</b></font>

222
00:18:15,004 --> 00:18:18,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--That's an Eight-Six.
--Is that him?</b></font>

223
00:18:20,644 --> 00:18:24,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, that was fun! Akina Pass is the best!</b></font>

224
00:18:24,814 --> 00:18:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's slow going straight,</b></font>

225
00:18:26,244 --> 00:18:29,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it corners like the
real thing, right, Takumi?</b></font>

226
00:18:29,584 --> 00:18:31,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

227
00:18:37,864 --> 00:18:39,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

228
00:18:39,994 --> 00:18:45,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you look at my Levin from a distance...</b></font>

229
00:18:45,504 --> 00:18:48,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...it does look handsome!</b></font>

230
00:18:50,404 --> 00:18:53,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My Levin is so cool!</b></font>

231
00:18:53,244 --> 00:18:57,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm glad I bought my Levin!</b></font>

232
00:18:57,114 --> 00:19:00,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm happy for you, too.</b></font>

233
00:19:02,784 --> 00:19:06,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--They're kids.
--It can't be them.</b></font>

234
00:19:06,224 --> 00:19:08,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The famous racer who beat the R32</b></font>

235
00:19:08,954 --> 00:19:10,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>couldn't be a little kid!</b></font>

236
00:19:10,854 --> 00:19:12,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way!</b></font>

237
00:19:12,864 --> 00:19:16,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How old are you kids?
I hope you have a license.</b></font>

238
00:19:16,864 --> 00:19:19,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Otherwise, I'll have to tell the police.</b></font>

239
00:19:19,204 --> 00:19:23,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, I do! I may look cute, but I'm 18.</b></font>

240
00:19:23,304 --> 00:19:26,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Who do they think they are?</i></b></font>

241
00:19:26,644 --> 00:19:30,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Stop tormenting them.
--I don't like it.</b></font>

242
00:19:30,174 --> 00:19:32,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A kid like him is driving an Eight-Six</b></font>

243
00:19:32,644 --> 00:19:34,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and acting like a street racer.</b></font>

244
00:19:34,754 --> 00:19:36,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You live around here?</b></font>

245
00:19:36,354 --> 00:19:40,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you happen to know the
famous Eight-Six of Mount Akina?</b></font>

246
00:19:42,654 --> 00:19:45,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't act dumb. We know you know him.</b></font>

247
00:19:45,594 --> 00:19:49,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I, uh, I've heard of him...</b></font>

248
00:19:49,594 --> 00:19:52,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but he probably won't be here tonight.</b></font>

249
00:19:52,104 --> 00:19:55,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Darn, we came all this way for nothing.</b></font>

250
00:19:55,334 --> 00:19:57,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's get out of here.</b></font>

251
00:19:57,004 --> 00:19:59,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I tell you what, kid.</b></font>

252
00:19:59,544 --> 00:20:03,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you wanna act like a racer,
at least try to look like one.</b></font>

253
00:20:03,714 --> 00:20:08,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I mean, look at this
Eight-Six with its ugly wheels.</b></font>

254
00:20:08,354 --> 00:20:10,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's embarrassing!</b></font>

255
00:20:12,284 --> 00:20:13,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Pitiful!</b></font>

256
00:20:13,684 --> 00:20:17,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And change the muffler,
'cause it sounds pathetic.</b></font>

257
00:20:17,924 --> 00:20:21,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you know anything
at all about an Eight-Six?</b></font>

258
00:20:21,864 --> 00:20:23,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, actually...</b></font>

259
00:20:23,694 --> 00:20:27,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...this is not an Eight-Six, it's an Eight-Five...</b></font>

260
00:20:27,404 --> 00:20:30,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...so a new muffler won't make any difference.</b></font>

261
00:20:30,374 --> 00:20:32,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm thinking of getting one, though...</b></font>

262
00:20:32,804 --> 00:20:34,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Five?</b></font>

263
00:20:39,144 --> 00:20:44,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No one carries new mufflers
for an Eight-Five anymore.</b></font>

264
00:20:44,384 --> 00:20:45,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nobody!</b></font>

265
00:20:45,784 --> 00:20:47,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm crying!</b></font>

266
00:20:47,224 --> 00:20:50,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never thought anyone would be
driving an Eight-Five in this day and age!</b></font>

267
00:20:50,894 --> 00:20:54,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It suits you well though, kid!</b></font>

268
00:20:55,294 --> 00:20:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Let's go.
--Thanks for the laugh, kid.</b></font>

269
00:21:16,054 --> 00:21:20,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't let any scooters tailgate you!</b></font>

270
00:21:23,924 --> 00:21:26,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's it! They're gonna pay!</b></font>

271
00:21:26,964 --> 00:21:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, do you mind if I drive your car?!</b></font>

272
00:21:30,034 --> 00:21:31,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But, Takumi!</b></font>

273
00:21:31,364 --> 00:21:33,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go to the passenger side. Hurry!</b></font>

274
00:21:35,374 --> 00:21:37,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you gonna do, chase them?</b></font>

275
00:21:37,374 --> 00:21:42,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is only an Eight-Five with
loose suspension and '70s tires.</b></font>

276
00:21:42,074 --> 00:21:43,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't matter!</b></font>

277
00:21:43,474 --> 00:21:45,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We don't have to do this, Takumi!</b></font>

278
00:21:45,384 --> 00:21:47,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't have LSD, either!</b></font>

279
00:21:47,984 --> 00:21:51,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Shut up and put on your seat belt!</b></font>

280
00:21:52,784 --> 00:21:55,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It may get rough,</b></font>

281
00:21:55,154 --> 00:21:57,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but just trust me, okay?</b></font>

282
00:21:57,624 --> 00:22:02,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I promise I won't crash your precious car.</b></font>

283
00:22:02,194 --> 00:22:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here we go!</b></font>

284
00:22:08,604 --> 00:22:12,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi! Ohh! Ohhh!</b></font>

285
00:22:12,544 --> 00:22:13,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>P... Please...</b></font>

286
00:22:13,844 --> 00:22:19,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Take good care of my Eight-Five!</b></font>

287
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

288
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sou tanin wa kaizai shinai</i></b></font>

289
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, tomaritakunai</i></b></font>

290
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gisei ni natta ai ga cry shite mo</i></b></font>

291
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Peak mezashite, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

292
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! Keikokuon wa so cheap!</i></b></font>

293
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sheep-tachi wa michi wo akero</i></b></font>

294
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

295
00:23:00,054 --> 00:23:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Easy na motivation subete wa simulation</i></b></font>

296
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nigetemitatte doko demo safety zone</i></b></font>

297
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:12,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nani ka wo te ni irete nani ka wo wasureteku</i></b></font>

298
00:23:12,004 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekai ga kowaretemo kawaranai</i></b></font>

299
00:23:15,934 --> 00:23:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beasty shout, dare no te ni sae oenai</i></b></font>

300
00:23:24,014 --> 00:23:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hageshii yume jikan sae mo ima koeteku</i></b></font>

301
00:23:31,384 --> 00:23:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, yami o harisaite iku</i></b></font>

302
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like a streak to the peak</i></b></font>

303
00:23:37,394 --> 00:23:43,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekaijuu no kogekitta yoru o keshiteku</i></b></font>

304
00:23:43,534 --> 00:23:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, michi o hiraiteku</i></b></font>

305
00:23:47,404 --> 00:23:50,074
